Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:16.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}彷彿一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:23.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲傷已煙消雲散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}為了不讓這份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:38.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我會一直在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}沒有淚水的明天過後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}會有溫柔的未來等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:53.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只屬於自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:05.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的時候攜手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}在現實(現在)中Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life會和你一同發現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:20.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}生而為人的證明 與促成邂逅的點滴
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.36,0:21:06.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}(Stay with you forever…)
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.08,0:21:16.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも続くような
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.33,0:21:23.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲しみはどこにもない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}その笑顔 曇らないように
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.22,0:21:38.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}いつでもそばにいるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}涙のない明日の先に
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}優しい未来はある
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.36,0:21:53.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}淡い 希望でも 信じよう
